 id="_f55a3187-ca7c-43bc-bd73-9fc2c97da1db">SA = solar absorptance.</li><li xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_98b7de68-2e27-4f62-8bb9-49370e2ece11" inv:numbering="continue"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_d64adbe6-604a-406e-a2de-9cebf08a5964" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> listed are for the labelled, declared <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_26c0e11e-4bc3-42cc-8a0b-d95bf1af246b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of insulation.</li><li id="_faf04457-37d7-43ec-9539-f834534b2363">X = not permitted.</li><li id="_2ca97f71-8a6e-4a38-94f9-44222bb420f8">This Table shows wall heights for single <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_ab4ffded-52de-4d4e-a1c1-0e6adca5be87" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> dwellings. For two <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_8b2ae6f3-220c-44a2-936e-d57a7db0f484" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> (or more) dwellings, add R0.25 to the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_beeb58d3-c34e-4ed9-a40d-d69930928fc7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> given in this Table, to a maximum <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_7cd534e8-5af2-42f2-8b10-a701961b101f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of R1.44.</li><li id="_cf2f655a-11bc-4d51-91ac-29003c512573">Where an overhang of &gt; 1200 mm is used, the values for &gt; 900 to ≤ 1200 apply provided no more than 15% of the total opaque wall area of the dwelling (excluding windows/doors) is covered by overhangs &gt; 1200 mm.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference>